    "desc": "Zserbó is an online bakery that offers customers home made pastries, cakes, breads and cookies with an exquisite Hungarian and Caribbean influence. Unique, gourmet desserts. Our focus is quality and concistency. We offer nationwide shipping in the US. Our products are baked the day they are shipped.\nwww.zserbobakery.com",
    "text": "Log In\n0\nFree delivery in Rockland, MA\n\n\nSHOP ONLINE\nTreat Yourself\nyou deserve it\nA rich, layered apricot and walnut pastry flavored with rum and glazed with chocolate.\nThis cake was invented by Emil Gerbeaud in 1884.\nIt is one of Hungary’s most unique desserts. \nSHOP ALL >\n\n ANITA BORBELY\nOWNER & BAKER\nAnita, the Owner/Baker, grew up in Hungary and started baking with her mother at a very young age. She went on to master many traditional family recipes passed down to her, zserbó being one of them. \nLiving in London, England for school and for work, and spending a lot of time in the Caribbean Islands, Anita has introduced several international recipes to her menu. \nZserbó’s freshly made pastries are infused with the delectable flavors of Hungary and the Caribbean. \n  Anita’s mouthwatering desserts are guaranteed to satisfy her customers’ palate. \n\"I cannot get over this bakery!\nThere's something for every palate.\" \nThe Zserbó touch\nQUALITY INGREDIENTS FOR QUALITY TREATS\nZserbó aims to offer customers exquisite bakery products with a Hungarian and Caribbean influence. We do not recommend our products to people with any form of food allergies. Some of our products may not be suitable for children due to alcohol content.\n contact\n  Zserbo Bakery is taking a range of important Covid - 19 protective measures to help our customers shop safely. If you have any questions, please contact us.\nTEL: 617-959-0672\nEMAIL: ZSERBOBAKERY@GMAIL.COM\nSubmit\nJOIN OUR MAILING LIST\nSubscribe Now\nShipping & Refunds\nOur Policy\n  DISCLAIMER\nAlthough we offer gluten free products (no added gluten), we do not recommend our items to people with Celiac disease due to the risk of cross contamination. Zserbo Bakery operates out of a shared commercial kitchen.  Some of our products contain nuts. We use walnuts, pecans, almonds, hazelnuts and coconut. It is recommended that individuals with any form of food allergies do not consume our baked goods.\n  ©2020 by ZSERBO BAKERY",
